Introduced Version
SENATE BILL No. 87
_____
DIGEST OF INTRODUCED BILL
Citations Affected: IC 22-5-1.7.
Synopsis: E-Verify requirements for public works projects. Requires
a public contract for services for a public works project to include
provisions: (1) requiring contractors and subcontractors of any tier to
verify the work eligibility of all employees through the E-Verify
program; and (2) requiring contractors and subcontractors of any tier
to provide the public agency and the general contractor, construction
manager, or CMc with the E-Verify case verification number for an
individual before the individual begins working on a public works
project.
Effective: July 1, 2026.
Goode
December 8, 2025, read first time and referred to Committee on Pensions and Labor.
